{"type":"message","id":"03d51204","parentId":"0c8ab087","timestamp":"2026-02-26T09:39:54.284Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying hello after a new session. According to the instructions:\n\n1. I need to read SOUL.md, USER.md, and memory files first\n2. Greet in my configured persona (if one is provided)\n3. Be myself - use defined voice, mannerisms, mood\n4. Keep it to 1-3 sentences\n5. Ask what they want to do\n6. If the runtime model differs from default_model in system prompt, mention the default model\n\nFirst, let me check the runtime info:\n- Runtime model: openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7\n- Default model: openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7\n\nThey're the same, so I don't need to mention the default model.\n\nNow I need to read the identity/personality files. Let me start by reading SOUL.md, USER.md, and check if IDENTITY.md exists.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-80c31cafa4293939","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-80aa395b2693abe8","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\USER.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":10860,"output":431,"cacheRead":3056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14347,"cost":{"input":0.0041268,"output":0.0007327,"cacheRead":0.00058064,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00544014}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772098778446}}
{"type":"message","id":"49edf50f","parentId":"03d51204","timestamp":"2026-02-26T09:39:54.306Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-80c31cafa4293939","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772098794301}}
{"type":"message","id":"3202e31b","parentId":"49edf50f","timestamp":"2026-02-26T09:39:54.320Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-80aa395b2693abe8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772098794315}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3ebf9bb","parentId":"3202e31b","timestamp":"2026-02-26T09:39:58.382Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting - the IDENTITY.md and USER.md files are still blank templates, so this is a fresh setup. I need to figure out who I am and who they are. Let me start a friendly conversation to establish identity.\n\nAccording to BOOTSTRAP.md, I should start with \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\" and then figure out the details together.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\n\nI see we're starting fresh — let's figure this out together."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":11277,"output":200,"cacheRead":3056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14533,"cost":{"input":0.00428526,"output":0.00034,"cacheRead":0.00058064,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0052059}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772098794321}}
