{"type":"message","id":"d0bc5a77","parentId":"3116bc2e","timestamp":"2026-02-26T09:47:13.934Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Even read operations fail with the same error. This confirms the service account key is invalid or expired. The user needs to regenerate the service account key in Google Cloud Console.\n\nLet me inform the user about this issue and explain what needs to be done to fix it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"The Google Sheets service account key is expired or invalid. I can't add apartment \"67 Wall 7O\" until it's refreshed.\n\n**To fix this:**\n\n1. Go to [Google Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com/iam-admin/serviceaccounts) → Service Accounts\n2. Find `service-account-sheets@sturdy-landing-384907.iam.gserviceaccount.com`\n3. Click the 3 dots → \"Manage Keys\"\n4. Delete the old key (if it's still there) and add a new JSON key\n5. Download the new key and replace the contents of:\n   `C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\google-sheets-api\\credentials.json`\n\nOnce you've updated the credentials, let me know and I'll add the apartment."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":2,"output":281,"cacheRead":23643,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23926,"cost":{"input":7.6e-7,"output":0.0004777,"cacheRead":0.00449217,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00497063}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772099218736}}
